fields.name: Floating Kicks
fields.description:
"Floating" Sneaker Displays made of durable 1/4" Clear Polycarbonate. Set of 12 mounts (each mount holds one pair of sneakers). This wall mount is a slick simple easy quick install solution to displaying your prized kicks. These are designed so the platform does not protrude beyond the front sneaker giving it that floating feel. Mounts have two drilled holes for screw mounting to the wall (hardware not included). If you wish to mount with adhesive mounting strips you can still do so by purchasing and installing your own. These do not come with any mounting strips. Sizing is as follows.

Standard size, US Men's 6-12= 3 inches wide and the platform is 8 1/4" long.
X-Large size, US Men's 13-16= 3 1/2 inches wide and the platform is 8 1/2" long.
